'''White wolf sentries''' are [[aggressive]] [[monster]]s found on the [[White Wolf Mountain]] near [[Taverley]]. They can be dangerous to low-leveled players. They are similar to [[White wolves]], but have a lower combat level.

==Locations==
*[[White Wolf Mountain]]

